{"tid":2478771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女子警署外搶警槍稱圖自殺  認罪等候精神科報告始判刑","createTime":"2021-04-07T10:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T11:34:16.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c692d48832647d39f23a59796871c4ee7bbbc33","tid":2478771,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:00:34.000Z","msg":"警員今年2月在大嶼山北警署門外處理案件時，遭路過的女子搶去身上佩槍，警員隨即將女子制服拘捕。涉案女子早前被控搶劫罪，案件今再訊，<span class=\"red\">控方改控她一項企圖無牌管有槍械或彈藥罪</span>。女被告認罪，求情透露患有強迫症及焦慮症，當日欲搶槍自轟，無意傷害他人。裁判官將判刑押後至本月21日，先替被告索取兩份精神科報告，其間被告須還押小欖精神病治療中心。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情透露，被告與患有抑鬱及強迫症的母親相依為命，是家庭的經濟支柱。而被告自2019年起亦就強迫症及焦慮症求診精神科。案發當日，被告因遭上司指摘工作表現不理想，情緒一時失落，欲開槍了結自己生命，絕無意傷害其他人或損毀他人財產。<br />\n<br />\n警員及後將她制服拘捕，被告於警誡下稱：「我唔開心，我想自轟。」"},{"pid":"acc6c991d5ef0ecb07dde5c476506ff24d004407","tid":2478771,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:00:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/A7AEYXANI5G6FARKVQR6HWPX4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FA7AEYXANI5G6FARKVQR6HWPX4E%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=eaf8adec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210407%2FA7AEYXANI5G6FARKVQR6HWPX4E%2F&h=e9c7504a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210407/A7AEYXANI5G6FARKVQR6HWPX4E/</a>"},{"pid":"a8fb13174c4653578fae504e3cd66d4d5d1d05f5","tid":2478771,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72dea168252d32329147791cf777da4199468b55","tid":2478771,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e6bf58e02f862ffd9c87dab8b9412226a4ca74","tid":2478771,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948c9c2f82b1be462d1071df1502c67bf48d3ce7","tid":2478771,"uid":323572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"好似Manchester by the sea咁"},{"pid":"d679a5d7f6ee7e2ed80da3fb1435b14c2a64acf9","tid":2478771,"uid":135710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"防搶槍袋都搶到出嚟 應該有plan過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c44f6bd2c29fcb7583c254cd33241c382f4ffd","tid":2478771,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}